{"id":231826226,"title":"大象杯的一些小問題","content":"我是來抱怨的QQ\n\n當初選擇這款杯子是看上以下幾點\n◎700ml可以買大杯飲料\n◎材質不是玻璃比較輕\n◎透明的可以洗乾淨\n◎可以插著吸管\n\n但這杯子拿到手後我覺得它跟其他手邊現有的東西相性很差\n◎附送的袋子很高\n要能邊走邊提著喝飲料只能裝大象杯，不太適合其他杯子\n◎杯子高度無法使用其他吸管\n我手邊所有的玻璃吸管都只能抵達杯緣，也就是只能使用它附的吸管\n但它的吸管實在………\n看看這切口\nhttps://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtj.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/QbhW189.jpg\n怎麼看都不是平的\n\n這杯子已經因為吸管切口問題、包裝問題延後一、兩個月了\n到現在吸管切口還是不平啊\n就算我不使用它的吸管想用自己的，它也無法跟其他現有正常長度的玻璃吸管相容\n難道我要為了這杯子去額外買吸管嗎？\n\n好吧\n所以砂紙能不能磨平塑膠吸管？","excerpt":"我是來抱怨的QQ，當初選擇這款杯子是看上以下幾點，◎700ml可以買大杯飲料，◎材質不是玻璃比較輕，◎透明的可以洗乾淨，◎可以插著吸管，但這杯子拿到手後我覺得它跟其他手邊現有的東西相性很差，◎附送的袋","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-09T14:11:19.878Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-09T14:11:19.878Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":65,"tags":[],"topics":["環保杯"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"實踐大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":62},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtj.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/QbhW189.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"696383a5-e54b-4263-b1c7-4098806b7252","url":"https://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtjl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtjl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtjl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-09T14:11:19.878Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-09T14:11:19.878Z"},{"id":"696383a5-e54b-4263-b1c7-4098806b7252","url":"https://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtj.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/7uGLxtj","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/7uGLxtjl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-09T14:11:1